DocAttribute.Name: DeltaT_Constant
DocAttribute.Documentation: Temperature change which is applied to the complete section of the structural member. A positive value describes an increase in temperature.

DocAttribute.Name: DeltaT_Y
DocAttribute.Documentation: Temperature change which is applied to the outer fiber of the positive Y-direction. A positive value describes an increase in temperature.

DocAttribute.Name: DeltaT_Z
DocAttribute.Documentation: Temperature change which is applied to the outer fiber of the positive Z-direction. A positive value describes an increase in temperature.
